    public abstract class AbstractLiveCycleMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
    Abstract LiveCycle mojo, defining connection parameters and providing an easy way to retrieve a ServiceClientFactory instance.

        Get the ServiceClientFactory for the given properties.
        Parameters:
        host - The host name/IP address of the destination LiveCycle server.
        port - The port number of the destination LiveCycle server.
        protocol - The protocol which should be used to communicate with the LiveCycle server. This can be EJB of SOAP.
        username - The user name used to login to the LiveCycle server.
        password - The password used to login to the LiveCycle server.
        Returns:
        the ServiceClientFactory for the given properties
        Throws:
        org.apache.maven.plugin.MojoFailureException - when one of the required parameters was not found.
